    "en": {
      "title": "Four Tamils \u200b\u200bwho went to Dhanushkodi as refugees",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four persons from Vavuniya district have reached Dhanushkodi as refugees this morning due to the severe economic crisis in Sri Lanka.",
        "The Marine Police rescued them and brought them to the Rameswaram Marine Police Station and are investigating.",
        "They said that they came to Mannar from Vavuniya and reached Dhanushkodi by boat from Mannar.",
        "It is noteworthy that 96 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bhave come to Tamil Nadu as refugees so far. (R)"
      ],
